data.description: Super cute 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom raised ranch with attached single car garage bay is ready for new owners. Absolutely beautiful natural hardwood floors, and detailed ceilings! It has low maintenance brick & stone exterior! Basement has a finished lower level room with the ability for a 2nd kitchenette or bar set up.  Large enough for entertaining or movie watching. Home has a lot of storage with multiple closets and shelving for those Costco runs! Located on a corner lot with a park across the street, easy access to the interstate, shopping and restaurants. Pre-inspected for peace of mind. Call for your tour today! AMA
